ivardefs.name: active
ivardefs.desc: Whether this schedule record is in active use, or should not be used (such as was entered in error).

ivardefs.name: actor_
ivardefs.desc: The resource this Schedule resource is providing availability information for. These are expected to usually be one of HealthcareService, Location, Practitioner, PractitionerRole, Device, Patient or RelatedPerson.

ivardefs.name: comment
ivardefs.desc: Comments on the availability to describe any extended information. Such as custom constraints on the slots that may be associated.

ivardefs.name: planningHorizon
ivardefs.desc: The period of time that the slots that are attached to this Schedule resource cover (even if none exist). These  cover the amount of time that an organization's planning horizon; the interval for which they are currently accepting appointments. This does

ivardefs.name: serviceCategory
ivardefs.desc: A broad categorisation of the service that is to be performed during this appointment.

ivardefs.name: serviceType_
ivardefs.desc: The specific service that is to be performed during this appointment.

ivardefs.name: specialty_
ivardefs.desc: The specialty of a practitioner that would be required to perform the service requested in this appointment.
